# ${projectName}

Adopter project scaffolded by `claustrum init`. Wires a claustrum
`Conductor` from in-memory test doubles so the runtime boots without
external services. Swap stubs for production providers as you grow.

## Quickstart

```sh
pnpm install
pnpm dev                  # boot the conductor and run one turn
pnpm conformance          # run the runtime invariant suite
```

