## Next steps

1. Replace `InMemoryMemoryProvider` with `@claustrum/memory-postgres`.
2. Replace `WebChannelStub` with `@claustrum/channel-web` (HTTP/WS) or
   `@claustrum/channel-whatsapp` (Twilio).
3. Replace `StubAdjudicator` with a real `Adjudicator` backed by your
   `@adjudicate/core` Pack.
4. Replace the toy planner with an LLM-driven planner reading a
   `ModelProvider` (e.g. `@claustrum/anthropic`).

The conductor's port interfaces are frozen at `@claustrum/core@0.1.0`;
swap one provider at a time without touching the cognitive loop.
